{"word":"H3013 - יָגָה - yâgâh - yaw-gaw' - Afflict","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָגָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>yâgâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>yaw-gaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Afflict"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சஞ்சலப்படுத்து, சஞ்சலப்படுவருத்தப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to afflict, to grieve, to suffer, to cause grief"},{"paragraph":"a) (Niphal) grieved, grieving (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to grieve"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) to cause grief, to cause sorrow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>grieve: - </i>afflict, cause grief, grieve, sorrowful, vex."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3013 - יָגָה - yâgâh - yaw-gaw'/3013\">H3013</a>, <a href=\"#/H3015 - יָגֹון - yâgôwn - yaw-gohn'/3015\">H3015</a>, <a href=\"#/H8424 - תּוּגָה - tûwgâh - too-gaw'/8424\">H8424</a>"}]}